Get free icons in Dotted design style

Dotted design is a consistent icon pack.

  • The graphics are created on an 80x80 px canvas.
  • As iOS icons, these are designed as outlines but decorated by 2 px dots.

This icon pack works well for applications, landing pages, websites, custom emails and newsletters, presentations, and infographics with a clear light design.

Download free Dotted icons in different themes for UI and graphic design. You can also edit the images you want right on the spot.

The free graphics are pixel-perfect to fit your design and are available in both PNG and vector.
